  <description><![CDATA[<p>Enjoying a quiet location just outside the village and surrounded by ski runs and winter walking paths, the Waldhotel National is beautifully-furnished in an alpine-style throughout and has excellent leisure facilities including large spa and indoor pool. The ski lifts are just next door and guests can ski back to the hotel, weather permitting.</p>]]></description>
